"index_reference": "5586: town",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A large concentration of dwellings, often walled, to be distinguished from the larger cities.</p>\n<h2>A town was a large concentration of dwellings</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam23:7\">1SA 23:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh19:50\">JOS 19:50</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:10\">MRK 6:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:4\">ACT 16:4</a></p>\n<h2>Town officials</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut16:18\">DEU 16:18</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg8:14-Judg8:16\">JDG 8:14–8:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut19:12\">DEU 19:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut21:3\">DEU 21:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut21:19\">DEU 21:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:15\">DEU 22:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut25:7\">DEU 25:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth4:2\">RUT 4:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:4\">1SA 16:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra10:14\">EZR 10:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:2-Luke18:3\">LUK 18:2–18:3</a></p>\n<h2>Town records</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth4:10\">RUT 4:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:3-Luke2:4\">LUK 2:3–2:4</a></p>\n<h2>Laws concerning towns</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev25:33\">LEV 25:33</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num35:4-Num35:5\">NUM 35:4–35:5</a></p>\n<h2>Town celebrations and worship</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut16:5\">DEU 16:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam9:10-1Sam9:14\">1SA 9:10–9:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:29\">1SA 20:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr28:25\">2CH 28:25</a></p>\n<h2>The town was a close-knit community</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth1:19\">RUT 1:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam4:13\">1SA 4:13</a></p>\n<h2>Towns associated with Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:54\">MAT 13:54</a> <em>Nazareth, his home town</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:31\">LUK 4:31</a> <em>Capernaum in Galilee</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:1\">LUK 8:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:4\">LUK 8:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:5\">JHN 4:5</a> <em>Sychar in Samaria</em></p>\n<h2>Wickedness in towns</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut13:13\">DEU 13:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:30\">JDG 6:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs2:23\">2KI 2:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr30:10\">2CH 30:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:34\">MAT 23:34</a></p>\n<h2>Judgment on towns</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut13:15\">DEU 13:15</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:2\">ISA 25:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs3:19\">2KI 3:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:11\">MAT 10:11</a></p>",
